dct_description_sm: 1 map : hand colored, dissected and mounted on linen; 56 x 90 cm

dressé au Dépôt général de la guerre sous la direction de M. Le Lieut.t général Pelet ; gravé L. Bouffard ; Scale 1:400,000 ; Map originally folded ; Includes hand-drawn colored border lines ; Label pasted on back: Algérie: en 9 feuilles, echelle de 1/400,000: Oran ; Relief shown by hachures and spot heights ; Paris : Dépôt de la guerre
